   <title>
      <keyword>synblk</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The syntax block (&lt;<keyword>synblk</keyword>&gt;) element
organizes small pieces of a syntax definition into a larger piece. The syntax
block element is part of the DITA programming domain, a special set of DITA
elements designed to document programming tasks, concepts and reference information.</shortdesc>
